cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "spark-llm-deployment-evaluation"
message: "If you use this evaluation methodology or agent toolkit in your work, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "wutonglab"
    name-particle: "wutonglab"
repository-code: "https://github.com/wutonglab/spark-llm-deployment-evaluation"
abstract: >
  A reusable methodology and agent toolkit for evaluating LLM deployment decisions
  on DGX Spark and similar GB10/Blackwell-class hardware. Includes decision
  frameworks for model selection, quantization choice (FP8 vs NVFP4), speculative
  decoding, and a multi-provider LLM agent that walks users through evaluating
  any model + hardware combination with optional benchmark validation.
keywords:
  - LLM
  - inference
  - DGX-Spark
  - GB10
  - quantization
  - FP8
  - NVFP4
  - speculative-decoding
  - MTP
  - vLLM
  - benchmarking
  - decision-framework
license: Apache-2.0
